    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Extinct order of fossil marine reptiles characterized by a broad, flattened body, often a small head often on long flexible neck, a short tail, and four large, paddle-like limbs, dating to the Jurassic and Cretaceous periods.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
